title: The Noble
summary: The Noble • 귀공자 • The Childe • Young Noble Manhwa Description: “Jin Taeha,” the successor of Korea’s leading company “Cheongu,” survived alone after a terrorist attack during a yacht trip with his family. He learns that his family was killed not by accident but due to power struggles among his relatives. Entering the “Salerno Family,” an Italian mafia family, he prepares for his revenge. After 17 years, he returns to Korea and finally begins his revenge.
